{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If there was control in the room, they made a certain sign on the grenade which we knew, we who took part, the few people who took part in the sabotage group knew, and then we could-- we could do something else.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to do something else to ruin the grenade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But they started it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was on a conveyor belt doing with some pliers putting on a Bakelite cap and then twisting it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I had to reinforce it with pliers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, I made sure that I make the movement, but I didn't put it on properly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I first of all tried to put it on slant so that I shouldn't be able to screw it properly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I made sure that I didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I felt that I was going mad on the conveyor belt, and so I go out, and at the first occasion when they asked for a volunteer to work outside.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was-- the job was called a horse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And from then I became a horse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "My job was when the grenades came off the conveyor belt, I had to put them onto a flat iron lorry, very heavy, iron lorry which was on wheels.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I had to put on two grenades, and each one weighed 25 kilogram.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "At the same time, I had to load it up with 14 grenades in a way that the grenades shouldn't roll off, because it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "One of my toes was squashed like that, and actually one of my fingers was also hit by a rolling-down grenade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So I had to be very careful not to.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
